{"tid":1687542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[究極獅鳥獸] 海地群眾上街促總統下台　男子向群眾開槍遭毆斃燒屍","createTime":"2019-11-02T02:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T03:07:24.000Z","uid":31637,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e0bf648a916c6b5c93eefcaee69a0073de4b90af","tid":1687542,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:15:04.000Z","msg":"海地反政府示威持續，首都太子港有數百名警員及其支持者周日（27日）亦發起示威，爭取政府調高工資。在一個要求總統莫伊茲下台的示威活動中，1名示威者中槍死亡，群眾之後將開槍男子打死後燒屍。<br />\n海地警方表示，一名暫未辨認身份的示威者中槍死亡，而向群眾開槍的男子被毆斃，之後更被燒屍。根據傳媒報道，當時在示威活動附近有數名蒙面的便衣警員向天開槍，其後有不明人士爆出數輪槍聲，位置正在遊行群眾所在區域的旁邊。<br />\n在示威活動開始前，有蒙面警員在海地國家警察總局表達不滿。有拒絕透露身份的警察受訪者稱，警員的薪金微薄，亦沒有保險：「我們有一張保險卡，但所去的每一間醫院都需要付錢。」示威者遊行期間，有部分參與了教會崇拜後的人群加入隊伍。<br />\n<br />\n革命無罪,獅鳥有理<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20191028/bkn-20191028181245601-1028_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20191028%2Fbkn-20191028181245601-1028_00972_001.html&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8DC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=cdcc0eb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20191028/bkn-20191028181245601-1028_00972_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"97d329f6dc618c101f103b5a64b8347537dc05c6","tid":1687542,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:16:45.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded8efe4e0da6b8ac17ba726a1c1a5546dd5e46c","tid":1687542,"uid":116054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:17:17.000Z","msg":"我哋要將太子站變成人哋太子港"},{"pid":"333171bada5b30e0047bf4de59331c46c2d1a6f3","tid":1687542,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"鶳"},{"pid":"cee0990b2bf9c0a208c4b5d468a4d823f7847055","tid":1687542,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:17:41.000Z","msg":"首都太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n112"},{"pid":"4b848cc44c3f6a5bbc00959e0b615dca61863aab","tid":1687542,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"所以我地真係要打斷關節、重擊春袋啦<br />\n唔好再打頭打背打手打腳"},{"pid":"c2a428eaa1a869db330832613f42abe86abac045","tid":1687542,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:20:25.000Z","msg":"香港人太善良"},{"pid":"6ea880571b00df14f0c3661cc05322c2602b3dba","tid":1687542,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2a428eaa1a869db330832613f42abe86abac045","tid":1687542,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:20:25.000Z","msg":"香港人太善良"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:21:18.000Z","msg":"好快又有人入黎話香港人太懦弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582bfbfbeaf351c41e006f5b045f40282506a87b","tid":1687542,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"海地係台灣邦交國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01bb6f4ae30de566473b1f1f4afaf5c60681487c","tid":1687542,"uid":311796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:22:05.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好再剩係爆江咁善良啦"},{"pid":"6f6ac882512621ac6a32619d05c2a1a487ef8284","tid":1687542,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"一次性鶳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c631de8008b211d9ca62fadb07ce51e362b8d831","tid":1687542,"uid":292267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"六四都有燒過幾條解放軍  都係打死人之後被人圍毆"}]}